snippet.title: UnDungeon - Release Date Trailer | #Xbox #PC November 18
snippet.description:
Undungeon is coming to PC and Xbox One on November 18th.
https://store.steampowered.com/app/928990/Undungeon/
https://www.gog.com/game/undungeon
https://tblink.co/UndungeonGamePass

Undungeon is a science fiction action role-playing game set in a distant future. You are a messenger, a Herald created by your dimension and sent to an ancient city of Archaban with a task of vital importance: collect six seals that belong to other worlds. As you are traveling through space and time, the Multiverse gets rocked by a devastating cataclysm of unknown nature, leaving you stranded in a barren alien land. 

Join the Undungeon community: 
Discord: https://discord.gg/undungeon
Twitter: https://twitter.com/UnDungeon
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/undungeon
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/undungeon
Tumblr: https://www.tumblr.com/blog/undungeon
Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/UnDungeon

#Xbox #PC
